Installation steps for corpus preparation tools for syntax-based TM

- download MXPOST (see ../MXPOST/README)
- download Collins' parser (see ../collins-parser.linux/README)
- download SLM-V2 (see ../SLM/README)

- modify ../MXPOST/tag3.sh (as instructed in ../MXPOST/README)
- modify ../collins-parser.linux/parse3.pl (as instructed in ../collins-parser.linux/README)

- make binary (cd src; make all)
- modify ./run-prep.sh (to set Base= directory)


- follow instruction ../README

